Republic American Corp said itbegan an offer to exchange a new issue of 9-1/2 pctsubordinated debentures due 2002 for a portion of its commonstock.    Republic said it is offering to acquire its stock at a rateof 17.50 dlrs principal amount of debentures per common share.    The offering, which expires on April 27 unless extended, isfor up to 2,250,000 shares, with the company reserving theright to accept three mln shares, Republic also said. Reuter&#3;